---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import heroBg from '../assets/gallery/terrace-1.jpg';
import terrace2 from '../assets/gallery/terrace-2.jpg';
import jacuzzi from '../assets/gallery/jacuzzi.png';
import bedroom1 from '../assets/gallery/bedroom1-1.jpg';
import bedroom2 from '../assets/gallery/bedroom2-1.jpg';
import kitchen from '../assets/gallery/kitchen1-1.jpg';
import bathroom from '../assets/gallery/bathroom1-1.jpg';
---

<PageLayout
  title="The Apartment | Blue Moon Apartment, Mandre"
  description="92m² semi-penthouse apartment in Mandre, island of Pag. 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, fully equipped kitchen, private Jacuzzi terrace with sea & sunset views."
  pageTitle="The Apartment"
  pageSubtitle="92 m² · 2 Bedrooms · Up to 6 Guests · 2nd Floor · Sea &amp; Sunset Views"
  label="Blue Moon Apartment"
  bgClass="ph-terrace"
  bgImage={heroBg}
>

  <!-- ═══ OVERVIEW ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="apt-grid">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Overview</span>
          <h2>A Semi-Penthouse Above the Adriatic</h2>
          <p>This modern, recently renovated semi-penthouse apartment sits on the 2nd floor of a quiet residential building in Mandre, offering stunning seaside and sunset views from its spacious terrace. With 92 m² of thoughtfully designed living space, it comfortably accommodates families and is ideal for up to 6 guests.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:1rem;">The open-concept kitchen and living room area creates a warm, sociable atmosphere — perfect for relaxing in between beach days, or for sharing long Adriatic evenings with the people you love most.</p>
          <div class="overview-stats">
            <div class="stat"><span class="stat__num">92</span><span class="stat__label">m²</span></div>
            <div class="stat"><span class="stat__num">2</span><span class="stat__label">Bedrooms</span></div>
            <div class="stat"><span class="stat__num">2</span><span class="stat__label">Bathrooms</span></div>
            <div class="stat"><span class="stat__num">6</span><span class="stat__label">Max guests</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <Image src={terrace2} alt="Terrace sea view" widths={[400, 700, 1100]} sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 50vw" style="width:100%; height:auto; aspect-ratio:4/3; object-fit:cover; border-radius:var(--radius); display:block;" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ THE TERRACE ═══ -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--soft-sky);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="apt-grid apt-grid--reverse">
        <div>
          <Image src={jacuzzi} alt="Terrace with Jacuzzi" widths={[400, 700, 1100]} sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 50vw" style="width:100%; height:auto; aspect-ratio:4/3; object-fit:cover; border-radius:var(--radius); display:block;" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Outdoor Living</span>
          <h2>The Terrace &amp; Jacuzzi</h2>
          <p>Step outside onto the spacious private terrace and you're greeted by a panoramic view of the shimmering Adriatic Sea and the breathtaking colours of a Croatian sunset. Whether it's morning coffee with the sea breeze or a candlelit dinner as the sun dips below the horizon — this is where memories are made.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:1rem;">The private Jacuzzi/hot tub on the terrace is the apartment's crown jewel. Unwind after a day at the beach while watching the sky turn gold, with nothing but the gentle sounds of the sea.</p>
          <div class="highlight-box" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
            <strong>♨️ Private Jacuzzi</strong> — ideal for adults to relax while kids are in bed, or for a romantic evening under the stars.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ BEDROOMS ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="apt-grid">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Rest &amp; Comfort</span>
          <h2>Two Bedrooms</h2>
          <p>Both bedrooms are furnished with large, comfortable beds and quality linens to ensure a restful night's sleep. There's ample wardrobe space, and the rooms are kept cool by the air conditioning system.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:1rem;">The layout works perfectly for two couples travelling together, or a family of four to six — each couple or set of parents gets their own private bedroom.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1rem;">
          <Image src={bedroom1} alt="Bedroom 1" widths={[400, 700, 1100]} sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 50vw" style="width:100%; height:auto; aspect-ratio:16/9; object-fit:cover; border-radius:var(--radius); display:block;" />
          <Image src={bedroom2} alt="Bedroom 2" widths={[400, 700, 1100]} sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 50vw" style="width:100%; height:auto; aspect-ratio:16/9; object-fit:cover; border-radius:var(--radius); display:block;" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ KITCHEN ═══ -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--warm-sand);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="apt-grid apt-grid--reverse">
        <div>
          <Image src={kitchen} alt="Kitchen" widths={[400, 700, 1100]} sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 50vw" style="width:100%; height:auto; aspect-ratio:4/3; object-fit:cover; border-radius:var(--radius); display:block;" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Cook &amp; Entertain</span>
          <h2>Fully Equipped Modern Kitchen</h2>
          <p>The open kitchen is equipped with everything you need for cooking — whether it's a quick breakfast or a full family dinner with fresh Pag lamb and local produce from the market.</p>
          <ul class="feat-list">
            <li>🍳 Stove &amp; oven</li>
            <li>❄️ Refrigerator</li>
            <li>🫙 Microwave</li>
            <li>🍽️ Dishwasher</li>
            <li>☕ Coffee maker</li>
            <li>🧊 Ice maker</li>
          </ul>
          <p style="margin-top:1rem;">A barbecue is also available on request — perfect for those long summer evenings on the terrace.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ BATHROOMS ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="apt-grid">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Two Full Bathrooms</span>
          <h2>Comfort for the Whole Family</h2>
          <p>Two full bathrooms mean no queuing in the morning. Each bathroom is modern and equipped with a shower. The apartment also provides a hairdryer and iron for your convenience.</p>
          <ul class="feat-list" style="margin-top:1rem;">
            <li>🚿 Two full bathrooms with showers</li>
            <li>💇 Hairdryer provided</li>
            <li>👔 Iron &amp; ironing board</li>
            <li>🫧 Washing machine for your convenience</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <Image src={bathroom} alt="Bathroom" widths={[400, 700, 1100]} sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 50vw" style="width:100%; height:auto; aspect-ratio:4/3; object-fit:cover; border-radius:var(--radius); display:block;" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ AMENITIES GRID ═══ -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--soft-sky);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
        <span class="section-label">Everything Included</span>
        <h2>Full Amenities</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="amenity-grid">
        <div class="amenity-group">
          <h4>🛏️ Bedroom &amp; Bathroom</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>2 bedrooms with large beds</li>
            <li>2 full bathrooms with shower</li>
            <li>Hairdryer</li>
            <li>Iron &amp; ironing board</li>
            <li>Washing machine</li>
            <li>Quality bed linen &amp; towels</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity-group">
          <h4>🍽️ Kitchen</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Stove &amp; oven</li>
            <li>Refrigerator</li>
            <li>Microwave</li>
            <li>Dishwasher</li>
            <li>Coffee maker</li>
            <li>Ice maker</li>
            <li>Full cookware &amp; tableware</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity-group">
          <h4>📡 Entertainment</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Free Wi-Fi in every room</li>
            <li>Cable TV in every room</li>
            <li>Air conditioning throughout</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity-group">
          <h4>🌿 Outdoor &amp; Extras</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Spacious private terrace</li>
            <li>Private Jacuzzi / hot tub</li>
            <li>Sea &amp; sunset views</li>
            <li>Barbecue (on request)</li>
            <li>Outdoor seating &amp; dining</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity-group">
          <h4>🅿️ Parking</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Private outdoor parking space</li>
            <li>Private garage (max W: 2.60m, H: 2.40m)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="amenity-group">
          <h4>📍 Location</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>200m / 2 min walk to the beach</li>
            <li>Grocery store across the street</li>
            <li>Fish market &amp; pharmacy 5 min away</li>
            <li>Town centre within easy walking distance</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ FAMILY CALLOUT ═══ -->
  <section class="section-sm">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="family-callout">
        <div class="family-callout__icon">👨‍👩‍👧‍👦</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Perfect for Families</h3>
          <p>Blue Moon Apartment is designed with families in mind. Whether you're a couple with two children or two families with small kids looking to share a holiday, the space, layout, and location all work perfectly for you. Up to <strong>6 guests</strong> are accommodated comfortably.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ CTA ═══ -->
  <section style="background: var(--ocean-blue); padding: 3.5rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
      <h2 style="color:white; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Ready to book your stay?</h2>
      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin-bottom:2rem;">Send us your dates and we'll confirm availability within 24 hours.</p>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-white">Send an Inquiry</a>
        <a href="/gallery" class="btn" style="color:white; border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">View Gallery →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</PageLayout>

<style>
  .apt-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .apt-grid--reverse > *:first-child { order: 2; }
  .apt-grid--reverse > *:last-child  { order: 1; }

  .overview-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .stat { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
  .stat__num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ocean-blue);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat__label {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .feat-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }
  .feat-list li {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }

  .amenity-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .amenity-group {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xs);
  }
  .amenity-group h4 {
    font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--ocean-blue);
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
  }
  .amenity-group ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }
  .amenity-group li {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    padding-left: 0.9rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .amenity-group li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    top: 1px;
  }

  .family-callout {
    background: var(--warm-sand);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--ocean-blue);
  }
  .family-callout__icon { font-size: 3rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .family-callout h3 { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .family-callout p { color: var(--text-muted); }
  .family-callout strong { color: var(--ocean-blue); }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .apt-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .apt-grid--reverse > * { order: unset !important; }
    .amenity-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .feat-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .amenity-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .overview-stats { gap: 1.5rem; }
    .family-callout { flex-direction: column; }
  }
</style>
